ygData.messageBody:
Greetings and welcome.  I have just recently switched to the new Tholleus Prexus (sp?) server from Brell Serilis where i have a 54 druid and 35 Bard.  I am playing a ranger and LOVING it.  For one thing, TP has only 30 rangers ;-)  It is an unloved class and the server is primarily filled with players in the upper 50s on other servers who miss low level play and want an untwinked server.
 
Group of 3-5 taking mummies in Nektulos - whoo! that was fun.  At 7 I pulled oracles and leggos (in small trains) from the castle in CB to a 7-10 group.  WHEEE that was even MORE fun!!!!
 
The only problem is that I'm getting readdicted.  Still, planes level play in newbie level dungeons has to be the most fun I've ever had in EQ.  I am so excited.  I got a MINO AXE!  That thing kicks serious behind ;-)
 
Lahstia, level 10 Ranger of Tunare
----- Original Message -----
From: Lilyana Stormseeker
To: EQ_women@egroups.com
Sent: Wednesday, October 11, 2000 6:37 AM
Subject: [EQ_women] Greetings everyone :-)

My name is Lilyana and I play a Level 45 Paladin on
the Karana server. I have been playing for 11 months.
I also have several additional characters. I'm very
excited about finding this list for the women of
Norrath. Please feel free to email me.

!~Lily~!
